# Maison Parfum Frontend Rules

## Architecture

Always follow this project structure:

components/
  ui/
  layout/
  sections/

## Existing Components

Prefer existing components before creating new ones:

- Button
- Container
- SectionTitle
- ProductCard
- Navbar

Do not duplicate functionality.

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS only
- No inline styles
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Use existing CSS variables
- Luxury premium aesthetic

## TypeScript

- Strict typing
- No any types

## Sections

All sections must:

- Use Container
- Use SectionTitle when applicable
- Be responsive
- Be reusable

## Code Quality

- Small reusable components
- Clean props interfaces
- Accessibility friendly

## Design Language

Brand personality:

- Luxury
- Premium
- Elegant
- Minimal
- Perfume ecommerce